                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/132448505/">小确幸</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">通俗易懂，结合作者管理企业的实际，讲的比较接地气</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1168787011">
        <div class="comment">
